Question 3️⃣ (Still Simple)

Create a REST API using Spring Boot that adds two numbers.

Endpoint
GET /add?a=5&b=3
Expected Response
8
Requirement

Use @RequestParam
----
@RestController
public class NumberController{
    @GetMapping("/add")
    public int addnumber(@RequestParam int a,@RequestParam int b)
    {
        return a+b;
    }
}
